  "original_title": "50,000 \u0bb0\u0bc2\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bicycle price above 50,000 rupees",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the purchase of bicycle and its spare parts has increased due to the fuel crisis.",
        "More and more people are looking for bicycle dealers in many parts of the country to buy bicycles.",
        "As the number of people buying bicycles has increased, so have the prices.",
        "As of now, the price of a normal bicycle has crossed Rs 50,000, according to vendors.",
        "Also, bicycles with new designs and different technologies are sold for up to one lakh rupees."
      ],
